com.estmob.android.sendanywhere.sdk

Interface SendTask.FileInfo

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.estmob.paprika.transfer.UploadTask.FileInfo
    Enclosing class:
    SendTask

    public static interface SendTask.FileInfo
extends com.estmob.paprika.transfer.UploadTask.FileInfo
    The interface to provide file information of sending files.

    You can provide your own implementation of SendTask.FileInfo for non-traditional files that cannot be represented as File, such as files starting with content://..

    See SimpleFileInfo in sample for the example implementation of traditional File.
